55
00:06:14,527 --> 00:06:16,230
Yeah, I'm hurting, man, I really need some money.

56
00:06:22,694 --> 00:06:24,849
$20 ain't going to make it this time, man.

57
00:06:24,954 --> 00:06:28,186
