I'm half blind. I'm crippled.

78
00:07:10,381 --> 00:07:11,215
Nobody will hire me.

79
00:07:15,838 --> 00:07:16,671
All right.

80
00:07:19,730 --> 00:07:23,587
You actually got me feeling sorry for you, Louie.

81
00:07:23,692 --> 00:07:24,527
There.

82
00:07:27,690 --> 00:07:29,080
Thanks.

83
00:07:29,184 --> 00:07:30,018
Don't mention it.

84
00:07:30,123 --> 00:07:32,138
Now, this better be good.

85
00:07:32,244 --> 00:07:37,943
In that warehouse on Lamar between Commerce and Canton.

86
00:07:38,047 --> 00:07:39,369
You know where that is?

87
