The warehouse, be there at 2,300 hours.

89
00:07:47,814 --> 00:07:52,228
Do you think it's wise to be driving this van around?

90
00:07:52,333 --> 00:07:54,001
Don't ever question me, Whitney.

91
00:07:54,105 --> 00:07:56,190
Do as you're told, and don't be late.

92
