108
00:08:51,801 --> 00:08:54,026
Yeah, I know.

109
00:08:54,130 --> 00:08:56,111
Hey, dinner smells great.

110
00:08:56,215 --> 00:08:57,085
I'm starving.

111
00:08:57,189 --> 00:08:58,197
When do we eat?

112
00:08:58,301 --> 00:09:00,942
It's almost ready, and don't you

113
00:09:01,047 --> 00:09:03,306
go stuffing yourself either, because I don't want

114
00:09:03,410 --> 00:09:05,635
you falling asleep on the sofa.

115
00:09:05,739 --> 00:09:07,580
I got other plans for you.

116
00:09:12,308 --> 00:09:14,115
Yes, ma'am.

117
00:09:14,220 --> 00:09:16,444
Now, let me finish dinner, OK?

118
