Not yet.

151
00:10:47,646 --> 00:10:49,106
Come on, Neil, get real.

152
00:10:51,887 --> 00:10:55,015
Look, you just have to count me out this time.

153
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:57,343
OK, fine, hey, I'm going to let you go.

154
00:10:57,447 --> 00:10:59,185
I'm going to run over there and check it out myself.

155
00:10:59,290 --> 00:11:00,958
BILL (ON PHONE): You sure, man?

156
00:11:01,063 --> 00:11:02,175
Yeah, no problem.

157
00:11:02,279 --> 00:11:03,356
