195
00:12:39,773 --> 00:12:41,023
We're early.

196
00:12:41,127 --> 00:12:44,812
I told you the deal goes down at 11:00.

197
00:12:44,916 --> 00:12:48,392
I can't believe you gave Lanky Louie $200.

198
00:12:48,496 --> 00:12:50,512
We need to get inside here.

199
00:12:50,616 --> 00:12:53,501
How do you want to do this?

200
00:12:53,606 --> 00:12:55,551
Through the use of high technology.

201
00:12:55,656 --> 00:12:57,117
[breaking glass]

202
00:13:00,591 --> 00:13:01,912
What?

203
00:13:02,018 --> 00:13:03,165
I don't believe you did that.

204
00:13:03,268 --> 00:13:05,736
It's just a little broken glass.

205
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:08,412
Which the city is going to have to pay for.

206
00:13:08,516 --> 00:13:09,767
Hey, forget the city.

207
00:13:09,872 --> 00:13:10,950
You pay for it.

208
00:13:11,053 --> 00:13:12,513
You gave Lanky Louie $200.

209
00:13:12,617 --> 00:13:15,433
You shouldn't mind shelling out for a pane of glass.

210
00:13:15,537 --> 00:13:17,066
[breaking glass]

211
00:13:29,718 --> 00:13:32,186
