578
00:37:42,871 --> 00:37:45,548
Detective Webber, Morgan County.

579
00:37:45,652 --> 00:37:46,591
Dallas?

580
00:37:46,695 --> 00:37:48,398
What can I do for you?

581
00:37:48,502 --> 00:37:50,170
We have reason to believe that one of your vans

582
00:37:50,275 --> 00:37:52,985
was used in the commission of a felony.

583
00:37:53,090 --> 00:37:56,323
One of our vans?

584
00:37:56,427 --> 00:37:57,678
I don't believe I got your name.

585
00:37:57,780 --> 00:38:00,528
