587
00:38:02,057 --> 00:38:04,142
Milo Truscott.

588
00:38:04,246 --> 00:38:06,019
Mr. Truscott is not here.

589
00:38:06,123 --> 00:38:07,756
He and an assistant took a horseback ride.

590
00:38:07,861 --> 00:38:09,564
I don't know when they'll be back.

591
00:38:09,669 --> 00:38:11,163
Anything I can do?

592
00:38:11,267 --> 00:38:12,380
The description of the truck that

593
00:38:12,484 --> 00:38:14,327
