604
00:38:39,837 --> 00:38:41,749
There's some pretty special ingredients in our sausage.

605
00:38:41,853 --> 00:38:45,294
We're real particular about who sells it.

606
00:38:45,399 --> 00:38:47,450
Oh, here's Mr. Truscott now.

607
00:38:47,554 --> 00:38:49,118
[horse whinny]

608
00:38:52,767 --> 00:38:54,088
What's up, Clint?

609
00:38:54,192 --> 00:38:59,858
Detective Farrow, Dallas Police, and, uh--

610
00:38:59,962 --> 00:39:02,464
Detective Webber, Morgan County.

611
00:39:02,569 --> 00:39:03,749
Detective?

612
00:39:03,853 --> 00:39:05,420
What's all this about?

613
00:39:05,524 --> 00:39:07,851
NEIL: Mr. Truscott, I believe that this truck was used

614
00:39:07,956 --> 00:39:10,737
