719
00:43:47,228 --> 00:43:48,132
[horse whinny]

720
00:43:51,052 --> 00:43:52,685
We'll be leaving now.

721
00:43:52,789 --> 00:43:54,040
I'm sure we'll talk again.

722
00:43:54,145 --> 00:43:55,223
