740
00:45:04,527 --> 00:45:06,787
I want you to keep tabs on Mr. Farrow.

741
00:45:06,891 --> 00:45:08,350
How about Speer?

742
00:45:08,454 --> 00:45:14,781
I want a word with Mr. Speer before he talks to Farrow.

743
00:45:14,885 --> 00:45:16,379
[phone ringing]

744
00:45:21,037 --> 00:45:22,046
Farrow speaking.

745
00:45:22,150 --> 00:45:23,470
Yes, Neil.

746
00:45:23,574 --> 00:45:26,633
Yes, this is Burton here.

747
00:45:26,737 --> 00:45:28,892
What did you find out about the pig farm?

748
00:45:28,997 --> 00:45:31,222
The truck is there.

749
00:45:31,325 --> 00:45:34,592
